    "title": "Transitions (Hard)",
    "body": "Transitions signal the logical link between ideas: contrast (however), cause and effect (therefore), addition (moreover), example (for instance). Decide the relationship first, then choose the matching transition.",
    "key_points": [
      "Identify the relationship between the two ideas.",
      "However/yet = contrast; therefore = result.",
      "Moreover = addition; for example = illustration."
    ]
